## Background Jobs

Move slow operations to background:
```ruby
# Slow operation in controller (bad)
def create
  @article.save
  send_notifications  # Slow!
end

# Use background job (good)
def create
  @article.save
  NotificationJob.perform_later(@article.id)
end
```

